posts.post_title: WTT: T206 Jordan Miscut for similar - TRADED!
posts.post_content: Believe it or not... I have a dupe.  Hoping to parlay this into an equally as nice miscut.  I really only want a miscut with the full name at the top... bottom name can be missing/partial/full.  I have a few other graded ones stashed away to trade as well.  Would also consider SGC 40s or low grade EPDGs.
